Entities
1) Users (DONE)
2) User Address
3) Categories
4) Products
5) Payments
6) User Orders
7) User Payments
8) User Cart
9) User Roles - MASTER, ADMIN, CUSTOMER (DONE)

1) admin role can do CRUD operations on products
2) Customer role can purchase products
3) Customer can view products, filter by category and product name
4) Customer can add product to cart.
5) Customer can view past orders.
6) Customer can make payments for a order.
7) Customer can delete account.
8) Customer can delete ADD/DELETE user role.
9) Master role can view all users, orders and all payments .